  "remarks": "\nIn his position as the Chairman of Minsk Regional Executive Committee, Aliaksandr Turchin is responsible for overseeing local administration. By doing so, he supported the actions of the Lukashenko regime to undermine the rule of law in Belarus, repress civil society and democratic opposition, contributing to serious human rights violations.\n",
